# 💼 Smart Resume Enhancer using Generative AI

A simple and powerful Generative AI tool that helps users enhance their resumes by generating professional summaries, polishing experience descriptions, and optimizing content for Applicant Tracking Systems (ATS).

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✨ AI-generated professional summaries
- 🎯 Skill-to-role content optimization
- 📄 Project description enhancement
- 🧠 Built using Python + Flask
- 🌐 Minimal web interface for easy use

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python 3.x
- Flask (Web Framework)
- HTML/CSS (Frontend)
- Generative Prompt Engineering

---

## 📷 Demo

![Smart Resume Enhancer Screenshot](https://via.placeholder.com/600x300?text=Smart+Resume+Enhancer+Demo)

---

## 🧑‍💻 How It Works

1. User fills in:
   - Name
   - Experience
   - Skills
   - Projects

2. AI enhances the input using custom prompts.

3. Enhanced resume content is generated and displayed.

